1. Theory of Reality
This will be an essay examining what reality is

A - Mental Construction of Reality
B - Language and Thought
C - The Social Construction of Reality

2. Theory of History.
This will be an essay exploring the history of the universe.

A - The Age of the Big Bang
B - The Age of the Star
C - The Age of the Planets
D - The age of Sentient Life
E - the Age of Conscious Life

3. Theory of Civilisation
This will be an essay exploring what civilisation is.

A - The language & scientific model emerge
B - The Birth of Philosophy 
C - The Age of Civilisation
D - The Social Construction of Reality
E – avoiding a metaphysical existential crisis
F - The Birth of the State
G - Mathematics and the Birth of True Science
H – Imaginary abstracts in civilisations

4. Theory of Morality
This will be an essay examining ideas around morality, good and bad, and the purpose of the universe

A - Creation stories and the Meaning of Life
B - Growing more complex
C - Sustainability as Good and Good as Sustainability

5. Theory of Sustainability
This will be an essay exploring how to live the good sustainable life
